  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hi there!\n\nAfter a bit more investigation, I found a trick that fixes the issue for my specific case, but I guess will be breaking widgets in SSR:\n\n```tsx\n// instantsearch/packages/react-instantsearch-nextjs/src/InstantSearchNext.tsx\n...\n  return (\n    <ServerOrHydrationProvider\n      isServer={isServer}\n      instance={instance}\n      ignoreMultipleHooksWarning={ignoreMultipleHooksWarning}\n    >\n      <InstantSearch {...instantSearchProps} routing={routing!}>\n        {/* Commenting this line stops the loop (obviously, as it is the cause...) */}\n        {/* isServer && <InitializePromise nonce={nonce} /> */}\n        {children}\n        {isServer && <TriggerSearch nonce={nonce} />}\n      </InstantSearch>\n    </ServerOrHydrationProvider>\n  );\n}\n```\n\nI realised I am not adding much to the conversation, but in the end, it is clear that the issue is isolated in that `InitializePromise` component.\n\nSo far I was not able to really understand 100% what it does, and therefore I was not able to debug and try to fix it. Claude was not able either, so I commented the line and now my app _kind of_ works.\n\nI'll share more info whenever I can.",
    "created_at": "2026-01-08T14:00:21Z",
