  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Following @Haroenv suggestions on my PR (thanks for your support), I've moved the fixes to the `searchkit` adapter: https://github.com/searchkit/searchkit/pull/1412.\n\nAfter doing the changes, I must confess they feel more simple in there, which is always a good thing.\n\nI am afraid that repo is not that well maintained as this one, so it may take time for the changes to be merged, but in the meantime I've used https://github.com/ds300/patch-package to patch the changes on my projects. They are working fine so far!\n\nSadly, I won't be able to do the same for the `typesense` adapter, I don't have the time and knowledge to build a demo project and try it for myself.",
